Darkchylde Sketchbook #1
Publisher:  Dynamic Forces
Publication Date:  March 1998

Artist:  Randy Queen and friends

What we've got here is a compilation of a lot of different sketches and layout designs I decided to hide away in a drawer and pull out one day solely for this purpose.  Some are roughs, some are finished pencils.  We wanted to include both to show the evollution from an idea to its eventual completion.  My roughs are always just THAT, roughs.  Often I just try to capture the energy I want the piece to have, and then make my alterations, refinements, and adjustments when the ACTUAL rendering takes place.  The cover for this sketchbook was an exclusive and original piece created expressly for the fan club by myself, and the amazing combined talents of Jason Gorder and Jimmy Yu.  We hope you like it!

Thanks goes to Talon for this release.

